The error occurs because the `bash` tool requires a `description` field as a string. To fix this, provide a clear description of the command you want to execute. For example:

```json
{
  "name": "bash",
  "arguments": {
    "description": "Run a specific command",
    "command": "your_command_here"
  }
}
```

Replace `"your_command_here"` with the actual command you want to execute. Let me know what you'd like to do, and I'll format the tool call correctly!
